getting-started/installation.title: Installation
getting-started/installation.description: Get Veloxx up and running in your environment quickly and easily.

getting-started/quick-start.title: Quick Start
getting-started/quick-start.description: Get up and running with Veloxx in just 5 minutes! Experience up to 4x performance improvements over traditional data processing with our SIMD-accelerated library.

intro.title: Welcome to Veloxx
intro.description: Veloxx is a lightning-fast, production-ready Rust library for in-memory data processing and analytics. With up to 4x performance improvements over traditional approaches, it provides a modern, ergonomic API that delivers exceptional performance while maintaining excellent memory efficiency.

performance-analysis.title: Performance Bottleneck Analysis
performance-analysis.description: Veloxx has excellent infrastructure but suffers from critical algorithmic bottlenecks that cause 10-95x slower performance compared to Pandas in certain operations. This analysis identifies the root causes and provides a clear optimization roadmap.

performance/benchmarks.title: Performance Benchmarks
performance/benchmarks.description: Veloxx delivers exceptional performance through advanced SIMD acceleration, memory optimization, and parallel processing. Our comprehensive benchmarks demonstrate significant performance improvements over traditional data processing approaches.

performance/competitive-benchmarks.title: Performance Benchmarks
performance/competitive-benchmarks.description: Comprehensive performance comparison between Veloxx, Polars, and Pandas across various DataFrame operations and data sizes.

performance/cross-language-analysis.title: Cross-Language Performance Analysis
performance/cross-language-analysis.description: Comprehensive performance comparison between Rust Veloxx (native) and Python Pandas implementations across identical operations and datasets.

performance/features.title: Performance Features Guide
performance/features.description: Veloxx is designed for maximum performance through advanced optimization techniques. This guide shows you how to leverage Veloxx's performance features for lightning-fast data processing.

tutorials/async_json.title: Async JSON I/O Guide
tutorials/async_json.description: This guide covers Velox's async JSON capabilities with practical examples.

tutorials/customer_purchase_analysis.title: Tutorial: Customer Purchase Analysis
tutorials/customer_purchase_analysis.description: This tutorial demonstrates a more advanced workflow with the Veloxx library, including reading data from multiple CSV files, joining DataFrames, and performing a group-by aggregation.

tutorials/general_tutorial.title: Veloxx Tutorial: A Quick Tour
tutorials/general_tutorial.description: This tutorial provides a quick tour of the Veloxx library, covering the basics of creating DataFrames, performing common data manipulation tasks, and using the library's more advanced features.
